Welcome to Xapian!
==================

Xapian is free software, licensed under the GNU General Public License
(version 2 or later).  You should find a copy of the GNU General Public
License in the file "COPYING" in the top level of this distribution of
Xapian.

See the file "INSTALL" for information on building and installing Xapian.
If you're wanting to modify Xapian itself or build sources from git,
then the contents of the file "HACKING" are recommended reading.

You can find downloads, mailing lists, git access, and other useful
resources on the Xapian website:

http://xapian.org/

There's also a wiki with user-contributed and evolving documentation:

http://trac.xapian.org/wiki/
